    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Act as an SEO blog writer.\n\nWrite a 1000-word blog post in clean HTML format.\n\nTitle: {{ $('Parsing').first().json.title }}\nKeyword: {{ $('Parsing').first().json.slug }}\n\nRequirements:\n- Use proper HTML tags: <h2>, <h3>, <p>, <ul>, <li>\n- Ensure all tags are properly closed\n- Do NOT break HTML\n- Do NOT minify or compress HTML\n\nStructure:\n- Title (H2)\n- Introduction\n- Key takeaways (bullet points)\n- Table of contents\n- Main sections with headings\n- Conclusion\n- FAQs\n\nSEO:\n- Use keyword naturally\n- Include keyword in first 100 words\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nUse these images in the blog.\n\nYou MUST include both images.\n\nImage 1 URL:\n{{ $json.data[0].photos[0].src.original }}\nImage 1 Alt:\n\n{{ $json.data[0].photos[0].alt }}\nImage 2 URL:\n\n{{ $json.data[0].photos[1].src.original }}\nImage 2 Alt:\n\n{{ $json.data[0].photos[1].alt }}\n-----------------------------------\n\nImage Instructions:\n- Place Image 1 after the introduction\n- Place Image 2 in the middle of the article\n- Use this exact HTML format:\n\n\n\n- Do NOT skip images\n- Do NOT change URLs\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nOutput:\nReturn ONLY valid HTML\nDo NOT include explanations\nDo NOT wrap in code blocks",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "1e647313-6fd6-4c3f-9f9b-f4763db57fd9",
      "name": "Copywriter AI Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "position": [
        3296,
        304
      ],
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
