    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Create a slug, blog post title, meta description, and SEO labels for the following blog post:\n\n{{ $json.data[0].title }}\n\nSlug Guidelines:\n- Keep it concise (4-5 words maximum)\n- Include primary keyword related to recruitment or HR\n- Use hyphens\n- Avoid unnecessary words\n\nTitle Guidelines:\n- No colon (:)\n- Include primary keyword\n- 50–60 characters\n- Clear and engaging\n\nMeta Description Guidelines:\n- 150–160 characters\n- Include keywords naturally\n- Action-oriented and engaging\n- Reflect blog content accurately\n\nLabels Guidelines:\n- Generate 3 to 5 SEO-friendly labels\n- Each label should be 1–3 words only\n- Focus on recruitment, HR, AI, hiring topics\n- Avoid long sentences\n\nOutput format:\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object with these fields:\nslug, title, meta, labels\n\nExample:\n{\n  \"slug\": \"ai-talent-acquisition\",\n  \"title\": \"AI in Talent Acquisition Trends\",\n  \"meta\": \"Explore how AI is improving hiring processes...\",\n  \"labels\": [\"AI Hiring\", \"Recruitment\", \"HR Tech\"]\n\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "f16a6603-9703-48b9-bb9a-d759c2993169",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "position": [
        2208,
        304
      ],
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "retryOnFail": false
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const rawInput = $input.first().json.output;\nconst cleaned = rawInput.replace(/```json|```/g, '').trim();\nconst jsonObject = JSON.parse(cleaned);\nreturn [jsonObject];\n"
      },
